des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : support@thpus.com.
Touchstone Fireplace app help you control Touchstone Home Products Electric Fireplace easily.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your electric fireplace or adjust the heat setting.
There’s no need to use your fireplace remote control or control panel - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Touchstone Electric Fireplace in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Touchstone Fireplace" app in Android or IOS app market;
(2) Register a Touchstone Fireplace account in our "Touchstone Fireplace" app;
(3) You need to have your Touchstone Home Products Electric Fireplace installed and powered on.
(4) Configure these devices in our "Touchstone Fireplace" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Touchstone Fireplace" skill;
(5) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, IOS or Amazon app market;
(6) Configure Amazon device with the "Alexa" app;
(7) Search "Touchstone Fireplace" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8) Click Enable skill of "Touchstone Fireplace", and you'll be navigated to Touchstone Fireplace login page;
(9) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10) Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on fireplace"
“Alexa, turn off fireplace"
“Alexa, change ember bed light on fireplace to orange"
“Alexa, set flame speed on fireplace to 5"
“Alexa, set temperature on fireplace to 76 degrees"
